snippet: Jack Eichel scored an unassisted goal, and Buffalo beat the visiting Columbus Blue Jackets to give Coach Dan Bylsma his first victory with the Sabres.
lead_paragraph: Jack Eichel scored an unassisted goal, and Buffalo beat the visiting Columbus Blue Jackets to give Coach Dan Bylsma his first victory with the Sabres.
